name: Furious Brawler
description: I will say it now rather than later. This is a warship that I intend to take into danger. If anyone has objections speak now or forever hold your peace and get off my ship.
author:
Himichi Thackery,
Captain of the KFS Almayer, final address to the crew before embarking to Nutria.

name: Incessant Gunnery Drills
description:
One rat, Two rat, 
great, now repeat that
author: Ratting Johnson, Krysan Federal Reserve
